content.text:
- **Feb 18, 2021 – Perseverance Rover Landing:** NASA’s Perseverance rover touched down safely in Mars’ Jezero Crater ([www.axios.com](https://www.axios.com/2021/02/18/nasa-perseverance-rover-lands-mars#:~:text=NASA%27s%20Perseverance%20rover%20successfully%20landed,river%20delta%2C%20making%20it%20an)), beginning its mission to hunt for signs of ancient microbial life and collect rock samples for future return to Earth ([www.axios.com](https://www.axios.com/2021/02/18/nasa-perseverance-rover-lands-mars#:~:text=landing%20completes%20a%20trio%20of,slated%20for%20launch%20in%202026)).

- **Apr 19, 2021 – Ingenuity’s First Flight:** NASA’s Ingenuity helicopter performed the first powered, controlled flight on another planet ([time.com](https://time.com/5954081/ingenuity-helicopter-flies-on-mars/#:~:text=NASA%27s%20Mars%20Helicopter%2C%20Ingenuity%2C%20successfully,and%20safely%20landed%2C%20marking%20the)), briefly hovering ~3 meters above the Martian surface for 40 seconds before landing back safely ([time.com](https://time.com/5954081/ingenuity-helicopter-flies-on-mars/#:~:text=managed%20a%20historic%20ascent,and%20safely%20landed%2C%20marking%20the)).

annotations.title: Touchdown! NASA's Mars Perseverance Rover Safely Lands on Red Planet - NASA
NASA’s Ingenuity Mars Helicopter Succeeds in Historic First Flight - NASA

content.text:
- **Feb 18, 2021 – Perseverance Rover Landing:** NASA’s Perseverance rover successfully landed in Mars’ Jezero Crater, marking the start of a mission to search for signs of ancient microbial life and collect Martian rock samples for a future return ([www.nasa.gov](https://www.nasa.gov/news-release/touchdown-nasas-mars-perseverance-rover-safely-lands-on-red-planet/#:~:text=California,Credits%3A%20NASA%2FBill%20Ingalls)).

- **Apr 19, 2021 – Ingenuity’s First Flight:** NASA’s Ingenuity Mars helicopter performed the first powered, controlled flight on another planet, briefly hovering above the Martian surface ([www.nasa.gov](https://www.nasa.gov/news-release/nasas-ingenuity-mars-helicopter-succeeds-in-historic-first-flight/#:~:text=Monday%2C%20NASA%E2%80%99s%20Ingenuity%20Mars%20Helicopter,helicopter%20via%20NASA%E2%80%99s%20Perseverance%20Mars)).
